    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Lightning flashes and thunder crashes. All creatures are partially obscured if they are more than 20 feet from you.</p>\n<p>If you travel for 4 or more hours during a Thunderstorm, roll a [[/r 1d20 #On a 1, you are struck by a lightning bolt dealing 3d12 lightning damage.]]. On a 1, you are struck by a lightning bolt dealing [[/r 3d12 #lightning damage]] lightning damage.</p>\n<p>Lightning and Thunder damage rolls have a +2.</p>\n<p>Also has the effect of @Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.weather-effects.Lt1CSKq515uB6CMn]{Rain}, @Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.weather-effects.SJOG1eCJndgc6YcI]{High Winds}, and @Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.weather-effects.QeEVRdRfl0Hwf4B2]{Heavy Clouds}.</p>",
